01.10 F N=0,20;D 2
01.20 Q

02.10 T %2,N,": "
02.20 I (N)2.6,2.6,2.3
02.30 D 3
02.40 D 4
02.50 R
02.60 T "0"!

03.10 S Z(1)=1;S Z(2)=2;S I=2
03.20 S I=I+1
03.30 S Z(I)=Z(I-1)+Z(I-2)
03.40 I (N-Z(I))3.5,3.5,3.2
03.50 R

04.10 S J=N
04.20 I (N-Z(I))4.3,4.5,4.5
04.30 S I=I-1
04.40 G 4.2
04.50 D 5

05.10 I (J-Z(I))5.2,5.5,5.5
05.20 T "0"
05.30 S I=I-1
05.40 I (I)5.8,5.8,5.1
05.50 S J=J-Z(I)
05.60 T "1"
05.70 G 5.3
05.80 T !
